<i>noun</i>: 요리 [요리], 그릇 [그륻] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요리 [요리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cooking</dd><br>
<dd>음식을 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making food.</dd><br>
<dd>2. dish</dd><br>
<dd>재료를 잘 갖추어 만든 음식.</dd><br>
<dd>Food made with well-prepared ingredients.</dd><br>
<dd>3. handling</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 어떤 일이나 사람을 자신이 원하는 대로 능숙하게 처리함.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) An act of managing something or someone skillfully as one wants.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>그릇 [그륻]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bowl; dish; container</dd><br>
<dd>음식을 담는 도구.</dd><br>
<dd>A utensil that holds food.</dd><br>
<dd>2. being capable; being qualified</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 어떤 일을 할 만한 능력이나 자질 또는 그것을 갖춘 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The ability or qualification to do something; or a person who has such an ability or qualification.</dd><br>
<dd>3. dish</dd><br>
<dd>그릇에 담긴 음식을 세는 단위.</dd><br>
<dd>The unit for counting the number of dishes that contain food.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>